OL,5,G0105 Jeff Beck: Live At Ronnie Scott's
OL,6,     FJeff Beck played five night at
OL,7,     FRonnie Scott's Club in Soho,
OL,8,     FLondon along with some special
OL,9,     Fguests. This is a record of those
OL,10,     Fnights.
OL,11,G0305 Jimi Hendrix: The Guitar Hero
OL,12,     FEric Clapton, Mick Taylor and
OL,13,     FSlash are among guitar stars
OL,14,     Fpaying tribute to Jimi Hendrix's
OL,15,     Fmagnificent talent and
OL,16,     Fshowmanship, as well as his
OL,17,     Fextraordinary legacy.
